hared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257860/extras/89618a251810aa0104041fdfe2ad3c24.poster.avif?t=1720820663\" width=626 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257860/extras/89618a251810aa0104041fdfe2ad3c24.webm?t=1720820663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257860/extras/89618a251810aa0104041fdfe2ad3c24.mp4?t=1720820663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全程配音：</h2><br>所有过场均全程配音。请在比之前更加浸入式体验克莉的故事的同时，欣赏配音演员们的表演吧。<br><br>* * *<br><br>多谢你们在2019年对《克莉》的支持。希望这部续作能够满足你们的所有期望。游戏愉快！",
